/**
 * A regexp-tree plugin to replace different range-based quantifiers
 * with their symbol equivalents.
 *
 * a{0,} -> a*
 * a{1,} -> a+
 * a{1} -> a
 *
 * NOTE: the following is automatically handled in the generator:
 *
 * a{3,3} -> a{3}
 */Comment.Multiline
